          "text": "Overview",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Implement the methods of this protocol when you want to customize the layout behavior and perhaps return different values for different items or sections. "
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "All of the methods in this protocol are optional, so you can implement only the methods you need to achieve the desired layout. If you do not implement a particular method, the flow layout object obtains default values from its own properties and applies them uniformly. Implement your methods in the object you assign to the "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nscollectionview/1528246-delegate"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " property of the collection view itself."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
